- "Nurtured by developers" refers to the developers of the games;
- "First bloom" refers to the release dates of the games;
- "Categories" refer to the genres of the games;
- "Thrive" refers to the platforms on which the games are available;
- "Player engagement metrics" refer to the total metric value and metric count from the `game_analytics` table;
- "Session counts" and "total session durations" refer to the number of sessions and total duration of sessions from the `sessions` table;
- "Achievement counts" refer to the number of achievements up to position 10 from the `user_progress` table;
